{"tid":1324853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（全面龜縮）不敢「直接對話」　林鄭取消出席所有活動","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:18:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2971063387e85137ebdf7603ba970711c6037b","tid":1324853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"反《逃犯條例》修訂一役遍地開花，有網民倡議於今年書展上，與擬出席開幕禮的特首林鄭月娥「直接對話」。特首辦回覆稱，由於改變行程，今年林鄭月娥不會出席書展開幕禮及其他活動。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥原本會出席明日下午書展舉行的開幕禮酒會，惟有網民於討論區表示，得知每年林鄭均會出席書展開幕禮，並打算到書展與她「直接對話」。<br />\n<br />\n惟特首辦回覆稱，由於改變行程，今年林鄭月娥不會出席書展開幕禮及其他活動，相信一班網民將會失望。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/352788/書展2019-網民倡-直接對話-林鄭取消出席所有活動</code></pre>"},{"pid":"633a9cac79fa43531cee1f1ff3d8b0be6d7c0358","tid":1324853,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">717(今日)銀髮遊行都要幫</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721要上街！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定性<br />\n三、釋放所有義士<br />\n四、追究警隊濫權<br />\n五、立即雙真普選<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"fadaebf3a60a4cfa478adf3f301759f0433ef45d","tid":1324853,"uid":79278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"算唔算直接拒絕咗&quot;會面&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6869c7e93dadd394b5b3106870259ddb77b682","tid":1324853,"uid":230890,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dce3b4d13d6d8c5a8e36cb7410cc322a06e98d1","tid":1324853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hk